reviewText: Bought because it had an early role by Sigourney, she doesn't a good job with a part not that well written - some of the comedy was  a bit broad for my taste.
For being an older movie it plays well. I am happy with this VHS. :)
A good, funny and SWEET movie. Both actors are just perfect in their roles and the translations is excellent. A unique movie that I am glad to have found it and purchased.
